title: Howard Stern Sternthology (Declassified Week Vol.2) Part 2
description:
Howard Stern Sternthology (Declassified Week Vol.2) Part 2  (02:38:43)


* Medicated Pete's Last Day – Howard bids his wacky intern Pete goodbye (5/27/2010). Followed by a "Declassified" about Ronnie's "ass treeks".
 
* Dave Chappelle - The comedian drops by for a hang with Howard (4/5/2001). Followed by a "Declassified" about the origin of "Welcome to my nightmare".
 
* Stump The Booey – Gary takes on a cocky guy named Drew in 80's music knowledge (11/21/2002). Followed by a "Declassified" uncovering some more famous drops from movies.
 
* Robin Apologizes – Robin learned that she had been emasculating men all her life (1/17/2012). Followed by a "Declassified" about her drop, "4 inches is fine!" 
 
* Caller Has A Fantasy - A straight male caller is having gay thoughts about other men and seeks Howard's advice (12/9/2014). Followed by a "Declassified" on JD calling Howard a "sucker!"

* Sal Defends Caputo – Sal stands up for the Long Island Medium (6/9/2014)
